662
01:32:50,000 --> 01:32:57,000
Well, it was a question. So, what we want to go. You know, if I was healthy, it was nowhere in the world. Everybody can beat me to stop me from making the team.

663
01:32:57,000 --> 01:33:09,000
You know, when I went to the games, I didn't go to the game for the medal. You know, by the time I decided I was going to the game, the reason why I went to the games opposed to staying home like Karim Karim.

664
01:33:09,000 --> 01:33:23,000
And I had a conversation one time and I told Karim, I said, man, you're the NBA. If you choose not to go to the games, you say I prefer to stay home for my studies. Who's going to question that?

665
01:33:23,000 --> 01:33:35,000
