667
01:33:46,000 --> 01:33:55,000
That's the main reason why I went. It wasn't about no medal. Only medal consciousness that I had is that I had to win any medal.

668
01:33:55,000 --> 01:34:05,000
To get on the victory stand, I didn't go there anticipating taking third. I was giving the medal to Tommy. But see, that's what God steps in.

669
01:34:05,000 --> 01:34:16,000
But God put Peter Norman there to make this thing solidified and stand. We got 50 million white people running on the planet.

670
01:34:16,000 --> 01:34:22,000
Out of 50 million white people, I don't think we found two to mass Peter Norman.

671
01:34:22,000 --> 01:34:25,000
